{
  "texts": [
    "It is a non-parametric test for the null hypothesis that the median of the differences in the matched pairs is equal to 0 42.",
    "This test has the test statistic and rank(|d i |), i = 1,.",
    ", n, denote the differences d i in the n matched pairs ranked by their absolute values 43.",
    "The T-statistic can be examined directly by using its own critical values or, for large values of n, utilizing the statistic which follows the normal distribution under the null hypothesis 4.",
    "The Wilcoxon signed-rank test can be performed with wilcoxon in scipy.stats in Python or wilcox.test(x,y, paired=TRUE) in stats in R."
  ]
}